---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Yard Metric"
  description="Yard Metric does not collect personal information, require accounts, or track users. All calculations happen locally in your browser."
  canonical="https://yardmetric.com/privacy/"
>
  <NavBar />

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/" class="breadcrumb-link">Home</a>
          <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
          <span class="breadcrumb-current">Privacy Policy</span>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="page-lead">Last updated: June 2025</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="prose">

          <h2>The short version</h2>
          <p>
            We do not collect your personal information. We do not require an account. We do not
            sell or share data with third parties for advertising. Your calculation history never
            leaves your device.
          </p>

          <h2>What we collect</h2>
          <p>
            Nothing personally identifiable. Yard Metric is a static website. All
            calculations run entirely in your browser using JavaScript. No calculation inputs,
            results, or usage data are transmitted to our servers.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your most recent inputs and calculation history are saved using your browser's
            <code>localStorage</code>. This data stays on your device and is never sent anywhere.
            You can clear it at any time through your browser settings or by using the
            "Clear history" button on any calculator.
          </p>

          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We do not use tracking cookies or advertising cookies. Your dark/light mode preference
            is stored in <code>localStorage</code> on your device only.
          </p>

          <h2>Third-party services</h2>
          <p>
            We load fonts from Google Fonts. When your browser fetches these fonts, Google's servers
            receive your IP address as part of a standard HTTP request. This is governed by
            Google's own privacy policy. No other third-party services, analytics platforms,
            or advertising networks are used on this site.
          </p>

          <h2>Server logs</h2>
          <p>
            Our hosting provider may retain standard web server access logs (IP address, browser
            type, pages visited, timestamps) for a limited period for security and operational
            purposes. We do not use these logs to identify individuals.
          </p>

          <h2>Children</h2>
          <p>
            This site is not directed at children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect
            information from children.
          </p>

          <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>
            If we make material changes to this policy, we will update the "Last updated" date
            at the top of this page. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes
            acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> and we'll respond
            as quickly as we can.
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
.container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
.section { padding: 64px 0 80px; }
.hero { background: var(--color-canvas); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); padding: 40px 0 48px; }
.breadcrumb { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-mute); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.breadcrumb-link { color: var(--color-body); text-decoration: none; }
.breadcrumb-link:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }
.breadcrumb-sep { color: var(--color-hairline-strong); }
.breadcrumb-current { color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 500; }
.page-title { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -1.8px; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.page-lead { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-mute); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.prose h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.6px; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.prose p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-body); line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.prose a { color: var(--color-link); }
.prose a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
.prose code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; background: var(--color-canvas-soft-2); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: var(--color-ink); }

@media (max-width: 600px) { .container { padding: 0 16px; } .page-title { font-size: 32px; } }
</style>
